-Einstein or Fermi-Dirac phase space distributions must be\nretained, and present several new results on relativistic thermal averages in\nan appendix.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2016 20:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Jun 2016 22:41:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-14"}
